###
### Mus API - bateria completa de pruebas
### Ejecutable con la extension REST Client de Visual Studio Code
###
### Notas:
### - Actualiza @gameId con el id devuelto por Crear partida.
### - En pares, usa GET /state para ver hand.phaseState.participants y el turnPlayerId real.
### - Para probar descartes con cartas reales, sustituye las cartas por las de GET /state.
### - El flujo de pares depende de las cartas repartidas; puede saltarse automaticamente a juego si nadie tiene pares.
###

@host = localhost
@port = 8080
@baseUrl = http://{{host}}:{{port}}/api/mus

### Cambia este valor por el gameId devuelto por Crear partida
@gameId = 15


### =============================================================================
### FLUJO 0 - HEALTH MANUAL BASICO
### =============================================================================

### Consultar estado de una partida existente
GET {{baseUrl}}/games/{{gameId}}/state
Accept: application/json


### =============================================================================
### FLUJO 1 - CREAR E INICIAR PARTIDA
### =============================================================================

### 1. Crear partida
### Copia el gameId devuelto y actualiza @gameId arriba.
POST {{baseUrl}}/games
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "players": [
    {"id": "P1", "name": "Luis", "type": "human", "team": "A"},
    {"id": "P2", "name": "Bot 1", "type": "agent", "team": "B"},
    {"id": "P3", "name": "Partner", "type": "agent", "team": "A"},
    {"id": "P4", "name": "Bot 2", "type": "agent", "team": "B"}
  ]
}


### 2. Iniciar partida
### Esperado:
### - status = started
### - phase = descartes
### - hand.phase = descartes
### - turnPlayerId = ""
### - hand.discardRound = 0 si ya esta incorporado
POST {{baseUrl}}/games/{{gameId}}/start
Accept: application/json


### 3. Consultar estado inicial
### Usa esta respuesta para ver cartas reales de P1..P4.
GET {{baseUrl}}/games/{{gameId}}/state
Accept: application/json


### =============================================================================
### FLUJO 2 - DESCARTES REPETIBLES Y CIERRE EXPLICITO
### =============================================================================

### 4. Descartes - primera ronda sin descartar cartas
### Esperado:
### - totalDiscarded = 0
### - phase pasa a grande
### - turnPlayerId = P1
### - hand.discardsClosed = true/1
POST {{baseUrl}}/games/{{gameId}}/discards
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "discards": {
    "P1": [],
    "P2": [],
    "P3": [],
    "P4": []
  }
}


### 5. Consultar estado tras cerrar descartes sin descartar
GET {{baseUrl}}/games/{{gameId}}/state
Accept: application/json


### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
### FLUJO 2B - DESCARTES CON MULTIPLES RONDAS
### Ejecutar en una partida nueva, justo despues de start.
### Sustituye las cartas por cartas reales devueltas por GET /state.
### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------

### 6. Primera ronda de descartes con cartas reales
### Esperado si totalDiscarded > 0:
### - phase sigue en descartes
### - turnPlayerId = ""
### - discardRound incrementa
POST {{baseUrl}}/games/{{gameId}}/discards
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "discards": {
    "P1": ["1O"],
    "P2": [],
    "P3": ["10C"],
    "P4": []
  }
}


### 7. Consultar cartas despues de primera ronda de descartes
GET {{baseUrl}}/games/{{gameId}}/state
Accept: application/json


### 8. Segunda ronda de descartes con cartas reales
### Sustituye las cartas por las actuales despues del GET anterior.
### Esperado si totalDiscarded > 0:
### - phase sigue en descartes
### - discardRound incrementa otra vez
POST {{baseUrl}}/games/{{gameId}}/discards
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "discards": {
    "P1": [],
    "P2": ["4C"],
    "P3": [],
    "P4": []
  }
}


### 9. Cerrar descartes despues de varias rondas
### Esperado:
### - totalDiscarded = 0
### - phase pasa a grande
### - turnPlayerId = P1
POST {{baseUrl}}/games/{{gameId}}/discards
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "discards": {
    "P1": [],
    "P2": [],
    "P3": [],
    "P4": []
  }
}


### 10. Consultar estado tras cerrar descartes
GET {{baseUrl}}/games/{{gameId}}/state
Accept: application/json


### =============================================================================
### FLUJO 3 - SALTAR DESCARTES Y JUGAR GRANDE DIRECTAMENTE
### Ejecutar en una partida nueva, despues de start y antes de /discards.
### =============================================================================

### 11. P1 envida a grande directamente sin pasar por /discards
### Esperado:
### - GameCoordinator normaliza descartes con totalDiscarded = 0, autoClosed = true
### - phase = grande
### - action envidar registrada
### - pendingBet.team = A
### - respondingTeam = B
### - turnPlayerId = P2
POST {{baseUrl}}/games/{{gameId}}/actions
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "playerId": "P1",
  "type": "envidar",
  "phase": "grande",
  "amount": 2,
  "payload": {}
}


### 12. Consultar estado despues de salto directo a grande
GET {{baseUrl}}/games/{{gameId}}/state
Accept: application/json


### =============================================================================
### FLUJO 4 - GRANDE
### =============================================================================

### 13. Grande - P1 pasa
### Ejecutar cuando phase = grande y turnPlayerId = P1.
### Esperado: turnPlayerId = P2
POST {{baseUrl}}/games/{{gameId}}/actions
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "playerId": "P1",
  "type": "pasar",
  "phase": "grande",
  "amount": 0,
  "payload": {}
}


### 14. Grande - P2 pasa
### Esperado: turnPlayerId = P3
POST {{baseUrl}}/games/{{gameId}}/actions
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "playerId": "P2",
  "type": "pasar",
  "phase": "grande",
  "amount": 0,
  "payload": {}
}


### 15. Grande - P3 pasa
### Esperado: turnPlayerId = P4
POST {{baseUrl}}/games/{{gameId}}/actions
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "playerId": "P3",
  "type": "pasar",
  "phase": "grande",
  "amount": 0,
  "payload": {}
}


### 16. Grande - P4 pasa y cierra grande
### Esperado:
### - se resuelve ganador de grande
### - suma 1 punto a su equipo
### - phase pasa a chica
### - turnPlayerId = P1
POST {{baseUrl}}/games/{{gameId}}/actions
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "playerId": "P4",
  "type": "pasar",
  "phase": "grande",
  "amount": 0,
  "payload": {}
}


### 17. Consultar estado tras cerrar grande
GET {{baseUrl}}/games/{{gameId}}/state
Accept: application/json


### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
### FLUJO 4B - GRANDE CON ENVITE QUERIDO
### Ejecutar en partida nueva tras llegar a grande.
### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------

### 18. Grande - P1 envida
### Esperado: pendingBet, respondingTeam = B, turnPlayerId = P2
POST {{baseUrl}}/games/{{gameId}}/actions
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "playerId": "P1",
  "type": "envidar",
  "phase": "grande",
  "amount": 2,
  "payload": {}
}


### 19. Grande - P2 quiere
### Esperado:
### - se resuelve grande
### - suma 2 puntos al equipo ganador real de grande
### - phase pasa a chica
### - turnPlayerId = P1
POST {{baseUrl}}/games/{{gameId}}/actions
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "playerId": "P2",
  "type": "querer",
  "phase": "grande",
  "amount": 0,
  "payload": {}
}


### 20. Consultar estado tras grande querido
GET {{baseUrl}}/games/{{gameId}}/state
Accept: application/json


### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
### FLUJO 4C - GRANDE CON ENVITE NO QUERIDO
### Ejecutar en partida nueva tras llegar a grande.
### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------

### 21. Grande - P1 envida
POST {{baseUrl}}/games/{{gameId}}/actions
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "playerId": "P1",
  "type": "envidar",
  "phase": "grande",
  "amount": 2,
  "payload": {}
}


### 22. Grande - P2 no quiere
### Esperado:
### - equipo A suma 1 punto
### - phase pasa a chica
### - turnPlayerId = P1
POST {{baseUrl}}/games/{{gameId}}/actions
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "playerId": "P2",
  "type": "no_querer",
  "phase": "grande",
  "amount": 0,
  "payload": {}
}


### 23. Consultar estado tras grande no querido
GET {{baseUrl}}/games/{{gameId}}/state
Accept: application/json


### =============================================================================
### FLUJO 5 - CHICA
### =============================================================================

### 24. Chica - P1 pasa
### Ejecutar cuando phase = chica y turnPlayerId = P1.
### Esperado: turnPlayerId = P2
POST {{baseUrl}}/games/{{gameId}}/actions
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "playerId": "P1",
  "type": "pasar",
  "phase": "chica",
  "amount": 0,
  "payload": {}
}


### 25. Chica - P2 pasa
POST {{baseUrl}}/games/{{gameId}}/actions
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "playerId": "P2",
  "type": "pasar",
  "phase": "chica",
  "amount": 0,
  "payload": {}
}


### 26. Chica - P3 pasa
POST {{baseUrl}}/games/{{gameId}}/actions
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "playerId": "P3",
  "type": "pasar",
  "phase": "chica",
  "amount": 0,
  "payload": {}
}


### 27. Chica - P4 pasa y cierra chica
### Esperado:
### - se resuelve ganador de chica
### - suma 1 punto
### - si hay pares: phase = pares, turnPlayerId = primer participante
### - si nadie tiene pares: phase = juego, turnPlayerId = P1
POST {{baseUrl}}/games/{{gameId}}/actions
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "playerId": "P4",
  "type": "pasar",
  "phase": "chica",
  "amount": 0,
  "payload": {}
}


### 28. Consultar estado tras cerrar chica
### Revisa hand.phaseState.participants si phase = pares.
GET {{baseUrl}}/games/{{gameId}}/state
Accept: application/json


### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
### FLUJO 5B - CHICA CON ENVITE QUERIDO
### Ejecutar en partida nueva tras llegar a chica.
### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------

### 29. Chica - P1 envida
POST {{baseUrl}}/games/{{gameId}}/actions
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "playerId": "P1",
  "type": "envidar",
  "phase": "chica",
  "amount": 2,
  "payload": {}
}


### 30. Chica - P2 quiere
### Esperado:
### - se resuelve chica
### - suma 2 puntos al ganador real de chica
### - pasa a pares o salta a juego si nadie tiene pares
POST {{baseUrl}}/games/{{gameId}}/actions
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "playerId": "P2",
  "type": "querer",
  "phase": "chica",
  "amount": 0,
  "payload": {}
}


### 31. Consultar estado tras chica querida
GET {{baseUrl}}/games/{{gameId}}/state
Accept: application/json


### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
### FLUJO 5C - CHICA CON ENVITE NO QUERIDO
### Ejecutar en partida nueva tras llegar a chica.
### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------

### 32. Chica - P1 envida
POST {{baseUrl}}/games/{{gameId}}/actions
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "playerId": "P1",
  "type": "envidar",
  "phase": "chica",
  "amount": 2,
  "payload": {}
}


### 33. Chica - P2 no quiere
### Esperado:
### - equipo A suma 1 punto
### - pasa a pares o salta a juego si nadie tiene pares
POST {{baseUrl}}/games/{{gameId}}/actions
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "playerId": "P2",
  "type": "no_querer",
  "phase": "chica",
  "amount": 0,
  "payload": {}
}


### 34. Consultar estado tras chica no querida
GET {{baseUrl}}/games/{{gameId}}/state
Accept: application/json


### =============================================================================
### FLUJO 6 - PARES
### =============================================================================

### 35. Consultar estado al llegar a pares
### Esperado si hay pares:
### - phase = pares
### - turnPlayerId = primer jugador de hand.phaseState.participants
### - hand.phaseState.eligibility indica pares/medias/duples/none
### Si no hay pares, esperado:
### - phase = juego
### - completedPhases.pares.status = skipped
GET {{baseUrl}}/games/{{gameId}}/state
Accept: application/json


### 36. Pares - participante actual pasa
### IMPORTANTE: sustituye playerId por el turnPlayerId real.
### Esperado:
### - turno pasa al siguiente participante, no necesariamente P2/P3/P4 secuencial.
POST {{baseUrl}}/games/{{gameId}}/actions
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "playerId": "P1",
  "type": "pasar",
  "phase": "pares",
  "amount": 0,
  "payload": {}
}


### 37. Pares - siguiente participante pasa
### Sustituye playerId por el turnPlayerId real.
### Si es el ultimo participante:
### - se resuelve pares
### - puntos: pares=1, medias=2, duples=3
### - phase pasa a juego
POST {{baseUrl}}/games/{{gameId}}/actions
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "playerId": "P3",
  "type": "pasar",
  "phase": "pares",
  "amount": 0,
  "payload": {}
}


### 38. Consultar estado tras jugar pares pasando
GET {{baseUrl}}/games/{{gameId}}/state
Accept: application/json


### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
### FLUJO 6B - PARES CON ENVITE QUERIDO
### Ejecutar en una partida que haya llegado a phase = pares.
### Usa el turnPlayerId real y luego el siguiente turnPlayerId real.
### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------

### 39. Pares - participante actual envida
### Sustituye playerId por turnPlayerId real.
POST {{baseUrl}}/games/{{gameId}}/actions
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "playerId": "P1",
  "type": "envidar",
  "phase": "pares",
  "amount": 2,
  "payload": {}
}


### 40. Pares - siguiente participante quiere
### Sustituye playerId por turnPlayerId real.
### Esperado:
### - se resuelve pares
### - suma 2 puntos al ganador real de pares
### - phase pasa a juego
POST {{baseUrl}}/games/{{gameId}}/actions
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "playerId": "P3",
  "type": "querer",
  "phase": "pares",
  "amount": 0,
  "payload": {}
}


### 41. Consultar estado tras pares querido
GET {{baseUrl}}/games/{{gameId}}/state
Accept: application/json


### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
### FLUJO 6C - PARES CON ENVITE NO QUERIDO
### Ejecutar en una partida que haya llegado a phase = pares.
### Usa el turnPlayerId real y luego el siguiente turnPlayerId real.
### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------

### 42. Pares - participante actual envida
POST {{baseUrl}}/games/{{gameId}}/actions
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "playerId": "P1",
  "type": "envidar",
  "phase": "pares",
  "amount": 2,
  "payload": {}
}


### 43. Pares - siguiente participante no quiere
### Esperado:
### - equipo del envite suma 1 punto
### - phase pasa a juego
POST {{baseUrl}}/games/{{gameId}}/actions
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "playerId": "P3",
  "type": "no_querer",
  "phase": "pares",
  "amount": 0,
  "payload": {}
}


### 44. Consultar estado tras pares no querido
GET {{baseUrl}}/games/{{gameId}}/state
Accept: application/json


### =============================================================================
### FLUJO 7 - CASOS NEGATIVOS DESCARTES
### =============================================================================

### 45. Descartes - faltan descartes de P4
### Ejecutar en phase = descartes.
### Esperado: MISSING_PLAYER_DISCARDS
POST {{baseUrl}}/games/{{gameId}}/discards
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "discards": {
    "P1": [],
    "P2": [],
    "P3": []
  }
}


### 46. Descartes - carta que no pertenece al jugador
### Ejecutar en phase = descartes.
### Esperado: INVALID_DISCARDS
POST {{baseUrl}}/games/{{gameId}}/discards
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "discards": {
    "P1": ["99X"],
    "P2": [],
    "P3": [],
    "P4": []
  }
}


### 47. Descartes - carta duplicada en el mismo jugador
### Ejecutar en phase = descartes y sustituir 1O por una carta real de P1.
### Esperado: INVALID_DISCARDS
POST {{baseUrl}}/games/{{gameId}}/discards
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "discards": {
    "P1": ["1O", "1O"],
    "P2": [],
    "P3": [],
    "P4": []
  }
}


### 48. Descartes - intentar descartar cuando ya se ha cerrado y phase = grande
### Esperado: INVALID_PHASE o DISCARDS_CLOSED
POST {{baseUrl}}/games/{{gameId}}/discards
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "discards": {
    "P1": [],
    "P2": [],
    "P3": [],
    "P4": []
  }
}


### =============================================================================
### FLUJO 8 - CASOS NEGATIVOS ACCIONES
### =============================================================================

### 49. Accion - jugar fuera de turno
### Ejecutar cuando turnPlayerId no sea P3.
### Esperado: NOT_PLAYER_TURN
POST {{baseUrl}}/games/{{gameId}}/actions
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "playerId": "P3",
  "type": "pasar",
  "phase": "grande",
  "amount": 0,
  "payload": {}
}


### 50. Accion - querer sin apuesta pendiente
### Ejecutar en cualquier fase implementada sin pendingBet.
### Esperado: NO_PENDING_BET
POST {{baseUrl}}/games/{{gameId}}/actions
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "playerId": "P1",
  "type": "querer",
  "phase": "grande",
  "amount": 0,
  "payload": {}
}


### 51. Accion - fase incorrecta
### Ejecutar cuando la fase real no sea chica.
### Esperado: INVALID_ACTION_PHASE
POST {{baseUrl}}/games/{{gameId}}/actions
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "playerId": "P1",
  "type": "pasar",
  "phase": "chica",
  "amount": 0,
  "payload": {}
}


### 52. Accion - fase no implementada aun
### Ejecutar cuando el estado ya haya llegado a juego.
### Esperado mientras juego no este implementado: PHASE_NOT_IMPLEMENTED
POST {{baseUrl}}/games/{{gameId}}/actions
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "playerId": "P1",
  "type": "pasar",
  "phase": "juego",
  "amount": 0,
  "payload": {}
}


### 53. Pares - jugador sin pares intenta jugar
### Ejecutar cuando phase = pares y el jugador NO este en hand.phaseState.participants.
### Sustituye playerId por un jugador con hasPares=false.
### Esperado: PLAYER_HAS_NO_PARES o NOT_PLAYER_TURN segun el orden de validacion.
POST {{baseUrl}}/games/{{gameId}}/actions
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "playerId": "P2",
  "type": "pasar",
  "phase": "pares",
  "amount": 0,
  "payload": {}
}


### =============================================================================
### FLUJO 9 - ORDAGO MVP
### =============================================================================

### 54. Grande - P1 ordago
### Ejecutar cuando phase = grande y turnPlayerId = P1.
### Esperado:
### - pendingBet.type = ordago
### - amount = 999
### - respondingTeam = B
### - turnPlayerId = P2
POST {{baseUrl}}/games/{{gameId}}/actions
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "playerId": "P1",
  "type": "ordago",
  "phase": "grande",
  "amount": 0,
  "payload": {}
}


### 55. Grande - P2 no quiere ordago
### Esperado MVP:
### - equipo A suma 1 punto
### - phase pasa a chica
POST {{baseUrl}}/games/{{gameId}}/actions
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "playerId": "P2",
  "type": "no_querer",
  "phase": "grande",
  "amount": 0,
  "payload": {}
}


### 56. Consultar estado final del flujo probado
GET {{baseUrl}}/games/{{gameId}}/state
Accept: application/json
